On Mon, 23 Jun 2003, Bart Daugherty wrote:

> I've been letting my wife drive my bus lately and she is complaining about
> the play in the steering wheel.  I only have about 5 degrees or so, but I
> guess I should replace it.  Anyone know a good source for rebuilt steering
> boxes?

Before you blame the steering box, check out the drag link, swing lever,
and tie rods.  I chased what I thought was a steering box problem for a
week until I noticed that it was really in the drag link.

George
